## Version 3.0.0 - Multi-User & Collaboration Enhancement (2025-08-24) ✅ **COMPLETED**

### 🚀 **MAJOR RELEASE: Enterprise Multi-User Collaboration Platform**

**Status:** ✅ **FULLY IMPLEMENTED AND TESTED**

This major release transforms the Business Scraper from a single-user application into a comprehensive enterprise-ready multi-user collaboration platform with advanced analytics, real-time collaboration, and robust security features.

#### **🏗️ Core Infrastructure Completed**
- ✅ **Database Schema v2.0**: 11 new tables with complete multi-user support
- ✅ **TypeScript Types**: 700+ lines of comprehensive type definitions
- ✅ **RBAC System**: 5 user roles with 50+ granular permissions
- ✅ **Authentication**: Multi-user auth with session management and security
- ✅ **API Security**: All endpoints updated with workspace-based authorization

#### **👥 Multi-User Features Completed**
- ✅ **User Management**: Registration, profiles, role assignment, team management
- ✅ **Team Workspaces**: Shared projects with collaborative scraping campaigns
- ✅ **Role-Based Access**: Admin, Manager, Analyst, Contributor, Viewer roles
- ✅ **Permission System**: Granular permissions with inheritance hierarchy
- ✅ **Member Management**: Team invitations, role assignments, access control

#### **🔄 Real-Time Collaboration Completed**
- ✅ **WebSocket Service**: Real-time collaboration with conflict resolution
