## 📋 Version Overview

This document provides a comprehensive overview of all versions of the Business Scraper Application, including release dates, major features, and compatibility information.

## 🚀 Current Release

### v1.8.0 - August 24, 2024
**Status:** ✅ **STABLE - SUPERSEDED BY v3.0.1**
**Type:** Minor Release - Major Performance Enhancement
**Compatibility:** Full backward compatibility with v1.7.x

#### 🎯 **Major Feature: Smart Performance Mode Auto-Detection**
- **Intelligent Optimization Engine**: Automatic dataset size detection and performance mode switching
- **Adaptive Thresholds**: 1K advisory, 2.5K pagination, 5K virtualization with user customization
- **Real-time Performance Monitoring**: Memory usage, FPS, and render time tracking
- **User Control & Override**: Comprehensive performance settings with preference persistence
- **Business Intelligence Preservation**: AI features maintained across all performance modes

### v1.7.1 - January 22, 2025
**Status:** ✅ Previous Production Version
**Type:** Patch Release
**Compatibility:** Full backward compatibility with v1.6.x

#### Key Features
- **🎯 B2C Industry Categories**: Added 3 new industry categories optimized for B2C users
  - Home & Lifestyle Services (20 keywords, 14 domain blacklist entries)
  - Personal Health & Wellness (24 keywords, 16 domain blacklist entries)
  - Entertainment & Recreation (27 keywords, 15 domain blacklist entries)
- **🔍 Enhanced Search Coverage**: Expanded from B2B-focused to include consumer-oriented businesses
- **🚫 Improved Filtering**: Industry-specific domain blacklists for better result quality
- **👥 Multi-User Support**: Categories now serve both B2B and B2C use cases

#### User Experience Enhancements
- **🎨 Enhanced Stop Scraping UX**: Dramatically improved feedback when stopping operations
  - Immediate visual state changes and status indicators
  - Animated progress bars with stopping states
  - Processing step tracking for stop operations
  - Completion summaries and toast notifications
- **📊 Status Indicators**: Real-time status dots (Active/Stopping/Idle) with color coding
- **✨ Better Visual Feedback**: Clear indication of scraping state transitions

#### Technical Improvements
- Enhanced industry configuration with consumer-friendly keywords
- Optimized search terms for local service discovery
- Improved domain filtering for consumer marketplace exclusion
- Enhanced state management and UI synchronization
- Improved scraping operation lifecycle handling

### v1.4.1 - August 19, 2025
**Status:** ✅ **STABLE - SUPERSEDED BY v3.0.1**
**Type:** Patch Release  
**Compatibility:** Full backward compatibility with v1.4.0  

#### Key Features
- Complete application rebuild and redeployment
- Docker production environment optimization
- Enhanced health monitoring and system validation
- Production configuration refinements

#### Technical Details
- **Node.js:** 18+
- **Next.js:** 14.x
- **Database:** PostgreSQL 16+
- **Cache:** Redis 7+
- **Deployment:** Docker Compose

